    {
      "id": "s1-client-content",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 840,
      "y": 975,
      "width": 660,
      "height": 220,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#7048e8",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2022,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 2022,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Chart rendering (Recharts — needs DOM/SVG)\n  - dynamic(() => import(...), { ssr: false })\n  - Avoids hydration mismatches, keeps initial bundle small\n\nInteractive state (FilterContext)\n  - URL-synced: ?state=CA&formulary=OPEN\n  - 200ms debounced updates\n  - Every chart re-renders when filters change\n\nStreaming chat (useChat() from Vercel AI SDK)\n  - SSE stream from /api/chat\n  - Real-time token rendering\n\nWhy 'use client' on data pages:\n  - They read from FilterContext (React hooks = client)",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Chart rendering (Recharts — needs DOM/SVG)\n  - dynamic(() => import(...), { ssr: false })\n  - Avoids hydration mismatches, keeps initial bundle small\n\nInteractive state (FilterContext)\n  - URL-synced: ?state=CA&formulary=OPEN\n  - 200ms debounced updates\n  - Every chart re-renders when filters change\n\nStreaming chat (useChat() from Vercel AI SDK)\n  - SSE stream from /api/chat\n  - Real-time token rendering\n\nWhy 'use client' on data pages:\n  - They read from FilterContext (React hooks = client)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
