      "text": "CI/CD Pipeline + Preview Deploys\n\nGitHub Actions runs full suite on every PR\nVercel preview URL before merge",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "s7-r3-next",
      "originalText": "CI/CD Pipeline + Preview Deploys\n\nGitHub Actions runs full suite on every PR\nVercel preview URL before merge",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
