      "locked": false,
      "text": "EVALUATION\n\n621 tests across 29 test files\n41 golden queries scored on 4 dimensions\n\n96.3%   answer correctness\n100%    hallucination-free\n100%    temporal correctness\n100%    discrepancy detection",
      "fontSize": 13,
