      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Auth + Row-Level Security                                   ~1–2 days\n\nNextAuth.js or Clerk for JWT sessions.\nPostgres RLS policies on entity_id.\nBiggest lift — but entity_id already threads every query,\nso RLS enforces what the code already does.",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
