      "text": "TOTAL: ~2–3 days (parallelized)\n\n✓  Green = hours (configuration, not code)\n✓  Orange = 1 day (additive layers on existing arch)\n✓  Teal = 1–2 days (real feature work, well-paved path)\n\nAll items parallelizable. None require rearchitecting.",
